    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The exterior paint retains a strong gloss, though there are a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small door ding consistent with regular use. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free, with only light wear on the driver's seat bolster and all electronics functioning as intended. Mechanically, the car is solid; the engine runs smoothly, the transmission shifts crisply, and it has a complete service history. This is a dependable, attractive vehicle that offers a great balance of quality and value for its next owner.",
