    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that\u2019s as reliable as your favorite pair of jeans? This car has been so good to me and it's officially ready for its next big adventure! It\u2019s in solid shape, runs like a dream, and has been well-loved and cared for over the years. It's the perfect companion for your daily commute or those fun weekend getaways. Come take it for a spin\u2014I think you're really going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 32500.0,
