    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically robust 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This unit delivers linear power through its individual throttle bodies and is mated to a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox. To address the chassis' known weak points, the rear subframe has been reinforced with plates, and the VANOS system has been overhauled with upgraded seals and a cryo-treated hub. The rod bearings were recently replaced as preventative maintenance. The suspension features a refreshed multi-link rear setup and Bilstein dampers, maintaining the car's legendary handling dynamics. While the exterior shows minor road wear consistent with its 'good' condition, the mechanical vitals are in excellent health, and the M-Variable limited-slip differential provides superb traction out of the corners. A true driver\u2019s spec for the purist who values engineering integrity.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
